    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • RefUpdate

        protected RefUpdate(Ref ref)
        Construct a new update operation for the reference.

        ref.getObjectId() will be used to seed getOldObjectId(), which callers can use as part of their own update logic.

        パラメータ:
        ref - the reference that will be updated by this operation.

      • tryLock

        protected abstract boolean tryLock(boolean deref)
                            throws IOException
        Try to acquire the lock on the reference.

        If the locking was successful the implementor must set the current identity value by calling setOldObjectId(ObjectId).

        パラメータ:
        deref - true if the lock should be taken against the leaf level reference; false if it should be taken exactly against the current reference.
        戻り値:
        true if the lock was acquired and the reference is likely protected from concurrent modification; false if it failed.
        例外:
        IOException - the lock couldn't be taken due to an unexpected storage failure, and not because of a concurrent update.

      • unlock

        Releases the lock taken by tryLock(boolean) if it succeeded.

      • setRefLogIdent

        public void setRefLogIdent(PersonIdent pi)
        Set the identity of the user appearing in the reflog.

        The timestamp portion of the identity is ignored. A new identity with the current timestamp will be created automatically when the update occurs and the log record is written.

        パラメータ:
        pi - identity of the user. If null the identity will be automatically determined based on the repository configuration.

      • getRefLogMessage

        public String getRefLogMessage()
        Get the message to include in the reflog.
        戻り値:
        message the caller wants to include in the reflog; null if the update should not be logged.

      • isRefLogIncludingResult

        protected boolean isRefLogIncludingResult()
        戻り値:

      • setRefLogMessage

        public void setRefLogMessage(String msg,
                             boolean appendStatus)
        Set the message to include in the reflog.
        パラメータ:
        msg - the message to describe this change. It may be null if appendStatus is null in order not to append to the reflog
        appendStatus - true if the status of the ref change (fast-forward or forced-update) should be appended to the user supplied message.

      • disableRefLog

        public void disableRefLog()
        Don't record this update in the ref's associated reflog.

      • getOldObjectId

        public ObjectId getOldObjectId()
        The old value of the ref, prior to the update being attempted.

        This value may differ before and after the update method. Initially it is populated with the value of the ref before the lock is taken, but the old value may change if someone else modified the ref between the time we last read it and when the ref was locked for update.

        戻り値:
        the value of the ref prior to the update being attempted; null if the updated has not been attempted yet.

      • setOldObjectId

        protected void setOldObjectId(ObjectId old)
        Set the old value of the ref.
        パラメータ:
        old - the old value.

      • setPushCertificate

      • forceUpdate

        public RefUpdate.Result forceUpdate()
                             throws IOException
        Force the ref to take the new value.

        This is just a convenient helper for setting the force flag, and as such the merge test is performed.

        戻り値:
        the result status of the update.
        例外:
        IOException - an unexpected IO error occurred while writing changes.

      • update

        public RefUpdate.Result update()
                        throws IOException
        Gracefully update the ref to the new value.

        Merge test will be performed according to isForceUpdate().

        This is the same as: 

         return update(new RevWalk(getRepository()));
        戻り値:
        the result status of the update.
        例外:
        IOException - an unexpected IO error occurred while writing changes.

      • update

        public RefUpdate.Result update(RevWalk walk)
                        throws IOException
        Gracefully update the ref to the new value.

        Merge test will be performed according to isForceUpdate().

        パラメータ:
        walk - a RevWalk instance this update command can borrow to perform the merge test. The walk will be reset to perform the test.
        戻り値:
        the result status of the update.
        例外:
        IOException - an unexpected IO error occurred while writing changes.

      • delete

        戻り値:
        the result status of the delete.

      • link

        public RefUpdate.Result link(String target)
                      throws IOException
        Replace this reference with a symbolic reference to another reference.

        This exact reference (not its traversed leaf) is replaced with a symbolic reference to the requested name.

        パラメータ:
        target - name of the new target for this reference. The new target name must be absolute, so it must begin with refs/.
        戻り値:
        RefUpdate.Result.NEW or RefUpdate.Result.FORCED on success.
        例外:
        IOException

        導入されたバージョン:
